1. *Onaj* pohod je bio uspešan. (That campaign was successful.)
2. Našli smo *onaj* ključ. (We found that key.)
3. *Onaj* čovek je bio veoma uspešan. (That man was very successful.)
4. Da li ste upoznali *onaj* novi učitelj? (Have you met that new teacher?)
5. *Onaj* auto je veoma skup. (That car is very expensive.)
6. Našli smo *onaj* put. (We found that path.)
7. *Ona* žena je veoma lepa. (That woman is very beautiful.)
8. Da li ste razumeli *onaj* članak? (Did you understand that article?)